Repo -> Repo: Defines CreateBookingRooms method in repository using injected DB and Logger
Repo -> Repo: Receives ctx (used for request lifecycle management) and bookingRooms to contaim a booking details
Repo -> DB: Executes GORM insert query to store booking record
